<https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/105001048/2025-26/evaluation> a ns1:EvaluationSystem ;
    ns1:evaluationDescription """In the Progressive Assessment option, students will be evaluated by an end-of-semester exam in the TOEIC test format in week 14 (100% of the grade). Participation in class or in online sessions will be positively considered in the evaluation.
The Global Assessment option will consist of a final written exam in the TOEIC test format (100% of the grade).
Extraordinary Assessment students will sit a final written exam in TOEIC format (100% of the garde)."""@es ;
    ns1:hasEvaluationTrial <https://guia-kg.skai.etsisi.upm.es/resource/105001048/2025-26/evaluation/trial1>,
